videos.description: Jordan McLaughlin lobs up a pass for Chimezie Metu who finishes it off with a big dunk for the Trojans.
videos.headline: USC's Metu gets big slam on alley-oop reverse

videos.description: Elijah Stewart sinks a corner 3-pointer to put USC within one possession in the first half.
videos.headline: USC answers with Stewart 3-pointer

videos.description: Duane Wilson lobs the ball up to Robert Williams who slams it down with two hands against USC.
videos.headline: Williams stuffs home the Texas A&M alley-oop
